      "rationale": "A systematic mesh refinement study was conducted using three mesh densities (3.2M, 8.7M, and 21.4M elements). Richardson extrapolation yields discretization errors below 3.8% for pressure head and below 4.2% for hemolysis index across all 5 operating points, meeting the 5% threshold."
