    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieve their required gradation levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at gradation 1 per the MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. Validation results demonstrate sufficient agreement between CFD predictions and experimental measurements for pressure head and relative hemolysis index across the CPB operating envelope. The model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions and supporting the regulatory submission decision.",
